formalpara.para:
For each title, PUL shall provide the following:
A title-specific markup addendum clarifying unusual zoning and structural features;
A sample copy (in PDF format) marked up according to the markup policy;
A marked up copy of any issue(s) deviating substantially from either the general or title-specific markup policies.
DDD shall work with PUL to produce these items. Modifications to the markup instructions or changes to the Blue Mountain docWorks configuration must be completed before DDD begins work on the batch.
